{"type": "article", "id": 12858, "title": "Nendo 可更换靠背椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-31T07:34:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122459hloevgmdHj51NJSI.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本设计工作室 Nendo 最近推出了一套新的椅子系列，白色铝制的椅子座简洁大方，而看似简单的椅子背正是玄机所在，他们为这款椅子设计了五种靠背，靠背和椅座之间可以自由拆分，自由组合，这些靠背有高有低，有连绵的怀抱，有跳跃的线条，采用木质材料，和白色椅架相得益彰。这是 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">Nendo 的主页</a>，点击可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140542BoAuUtnJm5gZIscF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405427cPFJi2kA16RmWyC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405436M9ufLpH2CczthZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140543I8ulc9FbxhaKsYUR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140544Gh1awbQC9fX0lHD5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140544CbuTUk4DYOp2KEeW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140545C9SZnYe3kJjFXcu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.38034188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}